proof_smt2:
(set-logic QF_LRA)
(declare-const f0 Real)
(assert (= f0 4.25e-05))
(declare-const f1 Real)
(assert (= f1 0.00010335013304297193))
(declare-const f2 Real)
(assert (= f2 -0.0002))
(declare-const f3 Real)
(assert (= f3 0.0002))
(declare-const f4 Real)
(assert (= f4 4.5e-05))
(declare-const A Real)
(declare-const B Real)
(assert (or (and (> f2 -0.00018) (= A 0.0)) (and (<= f2 -0.00018) (= A 0.0))))
(assert (or (and (> f2 -0.00018) (= B 0.0)) (and (<= f2 -0.00018) (= B 0.0))))
(assert (or (not (= A 0.0)) (not (= B 0.0))))
(check-sat)
robust_smt2:
(set-logic QF_LRA)
(declare-const f0 Real)
(assert (>= f0 4.05e-05))
(assert (<= f0 4.4500000000000004e-05))
(declare-const f1 Real)
(assert (>= f1 0.00010135013304297194))
(assert (<= f1 0.00010535013304297193))
(declare-const f2 Real)
(assert (>= f2 -0.000202))
(assert (<= f2 -0.00019800000000000002))
(declare-const f3 Real)
(assert (>= f3 0.00019800000000000002))
(assert (<= f3 0.000202))
(declare-const f4 Real)
(assert (>= f4 4.3e-05))
(assert (<= f4 4.7000000000000004e-05))
(declare-const A Real)
(declare-const B Real)
(assert (or (and (> f2 -0.00018) (= A 0.0)) (and (<= f2 -0.00018) (= A 0.0))))
(assert (or (and (> f2 -0.00018) (= B 0.0)) (and (<= f2 -0.00018) (= B 0.0))))
(assert (or (not (= A 0.0)) (not (= B 0.0))))
(check-sat)
